--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.12.0 (2020-12-03)
F: Add additional built-in alerting rules (system_status)

* Version 1.11.0 (2020-12-02)
F: Add built-in alerting rules
E: Clear predefined alerting rules (prometheus_alerting_rules)
E: Improve System Status dashboard (system_status)

* Version 1.10.0 (2020-12-01)
F: Add collection of built-in dashboards (prometheus_builtin_dashboards_state)
F: Add option to define Alertmanager URL (prometheus_alertmanager_url)
F: Add option to define Grafana URL (prometheus_grafana_url)
F: Add option to define Prometheus URL (prometheus_prometheus_url)

* Version 1.9.0 (2020-12-01)
F: Add Prometheus datasource 'Prometheus Alertmanager'

* Version 1.8.1 (2020-11-30)
E: Do not create home directory for service user

* Version 1.8.0 (2020-11-29)
F: Add option prometheus_monit_exporter_target_ansible_groups
F: Add option prometheus_monit_exporter_target_manual_hosts

* Version 1.7.1 (2020-11-27)
E: Improve Monit configuration file

* Version 1.7.0 (2020-11-26)
F: Update Prometheus to version 2.23.0

* Version 1.6.0 (2020-11-24)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (prometheus_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 1.5.0 (2020-11-16)
F: Update Prometheus to version 2.22.2

* Version 1.4.1 (2020-11-11)
B: Mark Prometheus datasource as default

* Version 1.4.0 (2020-11-10)
F: Add 'grafana' Ansible role dependency
F: Add Prometheus datasource to Grafana

* Version 1.3.0 (2020-10-15)
F: Update Prometheus to version 2.22.1

* Version 1.2.4 (2020-10-30)
